Make sure your Firebase project is set up:

Go to Firebase Console

Create a new project

Enable Authentication (Email/Password)

Create Cloud Firestore

Replace Firebase config in firebaseConfig.js with your project credentials.

Open index.html in your browser and test.


Firebase Hosting Deployment
Install Firebase CL

npm install -g firebase-tools
Login to Firebase

firebase login
Initialize Firebase

firebase init
Choose:

Hosting

Select your Firebase project

Set public directory as .

Say No to SPA rewrite

Deploy

firebase deploy

